Date: Wed, 1 Apr 2026 04:49:35 -0700
Subject: [PATCH] LineageParts: Add root access settings panel

Add SuAccessSettings fragment that lists installed apps with toggles
to grant/deny root (su) access. Writes UIDs to /data/system/su_whitelist
which the su binary checks on each invocation.

Accessible from Settings > Developer options > Root access.

Change-Id: I2e0461722f94442293b2787ab2a0296855819f15
